\n        </div>\r\n      <div class=\"text-layout \" >\r\n              \r\n    \r\n\r\n    \r\n\r\n    \r\n    \r\n    \r\n\r\n    \r\n    \r\n    \r\n<p class=\"star-wiki base-ellipsis clamp3 space-txt\"  vrcid=\"baike.498ee65\">        <span class=\"text-lightgray space-smlrspace\">1天前 -</span>\r\n<em><!--red_beg-->OpenClaw<!--red_end--></em>是一款由彼得·斯坦伯格(PeterSteinberger)开发的开源AI智能体(AIAgent)框架,曾用名Clawdbot、Moltbot,核心语言为TypeScript,以“蓝色龙虾”为标志性图标,Slogan是“TheAIthatactuallydoesthings”,即“真正能干活的AI”....</p>    \r\n    \r\n    \r\n    \r\n    \r\n    \r\n    \r\n    \r\n    \r\n    \r\n    \r\n    \r\n    \r\n    \r\n    \r\n    \r\n    \r\n<div class=\"citeurl \"  vrcid=\"citeurl.498ee65\"><span>战友集团山东公司</span><i>-</i><span class=\"\">weixin.qq.com</span><span class=\"cite-date\">- 2026-03-09</span>    </div>\r\n</div>\r\n      \r\n    </div>\r\n\n        </div>\n    <div class=\"r-sech ext_query r-sech-test_02 result_list click-better-sugg\" style=\"display:none\" id =\"sogou_vr_30010469_8\" data-async=\"1\" data-docid=\"ab735a258a90e8e1-6bee54fcbd896b2a-6402f695bcc695922be12a0d5172dfe7\" data-url=\"http://mp.weixin.qq.com/count/oIWsFt9PbX8iZPtrEB9QaNxa6cQ8/2247485780/1&amp;scene=6\"data-hint=\"sugg\"data-vrid=\"30010469\"data-rank=\"8\"data-title=\"%EE%90%8AOpenClaw%EE%90%8B%E7%AE%80%E4%BB%8B\"data-prevrid=\"11002601\"><span><strong></strong>推荐您搜索</span><i></i><p></p></div></div>\n<!-- z --><!-- a --><div class=\"vrwrap\" id=\"sogou_vr_30000000_wrap_9\"><h3 class=\"vr-title\"><!--awbg9--><a name=\"dttl\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"/link?url=LeoKdSZoUyAyguHHItJylysi_ilAVudjEoqFAKoUH5hEjciAtghiD9p8XosjjnYd\" id=\"sogou_vr_30000000_9\" cachestrategy=\"qcr:2,qcn:2_2_2_2_2_2_2_2_2_2\" bingpb=\"\"><!--awbg9--><em>openclaw</em>是什么- 深圳本地宝</a></h3><div class=\"fz-mid space-txt base-ellipsis clamp2\" id=\"cacheresult_summary_9\">深圳本地宝提供<em>openclaw</em>是什么有关的信息,<em>OpenClaw</em>(曾用名ClawdBot、Moltbot),被国内网友戏称为“小龙虾”,是由软件工程师彼得·斯坦伯格开</div>  <div class=\"citeurl\"><span>本地宝 </span><i>-</i